high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the kitchen sink
Pick up the right most knife from the counter in front of the sink
Turn around and walk to the white table
Use the knife to cut the green apple
Turn around and walk up to the cabinet right of the sink
Put the knife on the bottom shelf of the cabinet
Turn around and walk back to the white table
Pick up a slice of apple from the table
Turn around and walk up to the microwave above the sink
Cook the apple in the microwave then remove it
Turn right and walk up to the trash can left of the stove
Put the apple slice into the trash can
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked apple slice in the trash can

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sinks.
Pick up the knife that is in front of both sinks.
Turn around and walk to the white table.
Use the knife in your hand to cut the yellow apple on the counter that is in front of the big knife.
Turn around and walk to the pantry.
Open the pantry and place the knife at the front of the bottom shelf. Shut the pantry door.
Turn around and walk back to the white table.
Take the piece of the apple that is closest to the edge of the table.
Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple inside, close the door and heat the apple for a few seconds. Open the door and remove the apple; close the door again.
Turn right and walk to the gold garbage can on the floor.
Place the heated apple piece to the right of the toilet paper roll in the garbage can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple piece in a garbage can.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the refrigerator then turn right and walk to the sink.
Pick up one knife from in front of the sink.
Turn around and walk to the white table with the apple on it.
Cut the apple into thirds.
Turn around and walk to the cupboard on the right side of the sink.
Open the cupboard and put the knife on the bottom shelf then close the cupboard.
Turn around and walk to the white table behind you.
Pick up an apple slice from the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Cook the apple slice in the microwave above the sink then take the apple slice out of the microwave.
Turn right and walk to the gold trash can.
Put the apple slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw the cooked apple slice in the trash.

high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife on the edge of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to face the table.
Cut the apple on the table into three pieces.
Turn around and walk across the room to face the food cabinet.
Place the knife on the bottom of the food cabinet.
Turn around and walk forward to face the apple on the table.
Pick up a piece of apple on the table.
Turn around and walk across the room and look up to face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the trash can.
Place the piece of apple and place it in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple and place it in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the refrigerator, then turn right again and walk to the sink.
Pick up the knife at the edge of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the white table.
Slice the apple on the table.
Turn left and turn left again and walk to the cupboard.
Open the cupboard door and place the knife inside it.
Turn left and turn left again and walk to the white table.
Pick up the closest apple slice.
Turn right and turn right again and walk towards the microwave.
Open the microwave and place the apple slice inside, set the microwave for seven seconds and wait seven seconds, then take the apple out of the microwave.
Turn right towards the white table, then turn left and walk to the trash can.
Place the apple slice in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a microwaved apple slice.
